Reminder that EECS WHM is having industry office hours with Human Capital starting at 4:30pm today, followed by office hours with Ambi Robotics at 5:30pm! Everyone is welcome! Drop by to ask any questions about these companies and talk to their recruiters and employees! If you attend, you will be entered into a raffle to win a Google Home Mini, Google swag bag, Amazon Prime subscription, Fujifilm camera, or a waterproof speaker!

Human Capital OH: https://tinyurl.com/humancapital-oh 4:30-5:30 pm PT

Learn more: https://www.facebook.com/events/188350852719281

Ambi Robotics OH: https://tinyurl.com/ambi-oh 5:30-6:30 pm PT

Learn more: https://www.facebook.com/events/437969797476836

Join our discord to ask any other questions! https://tinyurl.com/eecswhm2021
